columns.expression: CASE WHEN state = 'CA' THEN num ELSE 0 END

queriesData.query:
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('quarter', ds) AS __timestamp,
       state AS state,
       gender AS gender,
       name AS name,
       SUM(num) AS sum__num,
       sum(num_girls) AS "SUM(num_girls)",
       sum(num_boys) AS "SUM(num_boys)",
       sum(num_boys) AS pct_boys
FROM birth_names
GROUP BY state,
         gender,
         name,
         DATE_TRUNC('quarter', ds)
LIMIT 1000
